---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";

const lastUpdated = "May 6, 2026";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Terms of Service — TNext Cigar"
  description="Terms governing your use of TNext Cigar."
>
  <section class="container-prose pt-20 md:pt-32 pb-24">
    <p class="eyebrow mb-4">Legal</p>
    <h1 class="font-display text-4xl md:text-6xl leading-tight">Terms of Service</h1>
    <p class="text-sm text-[color:var(--color-text-muted)] mt-4 uppercase tracking-wider">Last updated: {lastUpdated}</p>

    <div class="prose mt-12">
      <h2>1. Who we are</h2>
      <p>
        TNext Cigar is an independent editorial publication about cigars, owned and operated by Cris Ortiz Suárez. By using <a href="https://thenextcigar.com">thenextcigar.com</a>, you agree to these terms.
      </p>

      <h2>2. Age requirement</h2>
      <p>
        This site contains content about tobacco products. <strong>You must be at least 21 years old</strong> (or the legal age for tobacco-related content in your jurisdiction) to use this site. If you're under 21, please leave.
      </p>

      <h2>3. Editorial content</h2>
      <p>
        Articles, reviews, and opinions on this site reflect the views of the editor at the time of publication. We strive for accuracy but make no warranties. If you spot an error, email <a href="mailto:contact@thenextcigar.com">contact@thenextcigar.com</a> and we'll review it.
      </p>

      <h2>4. We don't sell tobacco</h2>
      <p>
        TNext Cigar is a publication, not a retailer. We do not sell cigars or any tobacco products. We do not ship tobacco. Cigars referenced in our editorial are linked to licensed retailers when available; those retailers handle the sale, age verification, taxes, and shipping under their own terms.
      </p>

      <h2>5. Affiliate disclosures</h2>
      <p>
        Some outbound links to retailers and brands are affiliate links. If you click and purchase, we may receive a commission. This never affects our editorial coverage. Articles that contain affiliate links carry a disclosure at the top.
      </p>

      <h2>6. Shop products</h2>
      <p>
        Where we sell directly (currently: branded merchandise, accessories, digital products) the sale is governed by the checkout terms shown at purchase. <strong>We do not sell tobacco products.</strong> Returns and refunds for shop items follow the policy displayed at checkout. Digital products (PDFs, courses) are non-refundable once accessed.
      </p>

      <h2>7. User submissions</h2>
      <p>
        If you submit a story tip, comment, or any other content to us via email, contact form, or future commenting system, you grant us a non-exclusive, worldwide, royalty-free license to publish that content with your name, edit it for clarity, or decline to publish it. We won't share your submission with third parties without consent.
      </p>

      <h2>8. Intellectual property</h2>
      <p>
        All editorial content, photography (where created by us), branding, and design on this site is owned by TNext Cigar. You may quote brief excerpts (under 200 words) with a clear attribution and a link back. Republishing whole articles, images, or design is not permitted without written permission.
      </p>

      <h2>9. Disclaimers</h2>
      <p>
        Cigar smoking carries health risks. Nothing on this site is medical advice. We are not lawyers, accountants, or financial advisors; nothing on this site is legal, tax, or financial advice. Consult relevant professionals as needed.
      </p>

      <h2>10. Limitation of liability</h2>
      <p>
        TNext Cigar is provided "as-is." We're not liable for any damages arising from your use of the site, the accuracy of content, links to third-party sites, or transactions you make with retailers we link to.
      </p>

      <h2>11. Governing law</h2>
      <p>
        These terms are governed by the laws of the State of Florida, USA, where the editorial office is based. Any dispute will be resolved in the appropriate Florida courts.
      </p>

      <h2>12. Changes</h2>
      <p>
        We may update these terms as the site evolves. The "Last updated" date is the source of truth. Continuing to use the site after changes means you accept the updated terms.
      </p>

      <h2>13. Contact</h2>
      <p>
        Questions about these terms? Email <a href="mailto:contact@thenextcigar.com">contact@thenextcigar.com</a>.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
